gobblin.runtime.commit

Class FsCommitSequenceStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.commit.FsCommitSequenceStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommitSequenceStore

    @Alpha
public class FsCommitSequenceStore
extends Object
implements CommitSequenceStore
    An implementation of CommitSequenceStore backed by a FileSystem.

    This implementation serializes a CommitSequence along with all its CommitSteps into a JSON string using Gson. Thus it requires that all CommitSteps can be serialized and deserialized with Gson.
